; 宿屋の一室
@saveon
@fg c=フレデリカ e=通常 f=03 b
@bg f=0001
@mu f=guild
[texton w=1]
[テオ e=通常 f=02]「[フレデリカ], good to see you today.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd176 f=03]「Yes, looking forward to staying with you～!」[k]
When I said hello, [フレデリカ] replied in a cheerful voice.[k]
She is a very bright and honest girl, although her laid-back nature is a bit of a drawback. As a leader, I am very grateful to have her.[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=01
[フレデリカ v=vd177 f=01]「You know, I'm really enjoying my current adventure!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Oh, what have you enjoyed so far?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd178 f=22]「Let's see... I've been to a lot of towns, and I've eaten some great food there...」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd179 f=23]「I came from a dwarven village deep in the mountains, so everything I see is new to me. So every day is fun...」[k]
Come to think of it, you said something like that before. You had never left your village until you became an adventurer.[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd180 f=21]「It's all thanks to you recruiting me at the guild.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd181 f=23]「If you hadn't, I would have had to give up being an adventurer and return to my village. Thank you, Captain!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「You've been a great help to me as well. Thanks again, [フレデリカ]!」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd182 f=04]「Heh heh heh... You're welcome...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「So, what are some of the best places you've been to?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd183 f=02]「Well... so far...」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd184 f=03]「Ah! I was so impressed with the steak restaurant on the main street in Sapphire City. That was so good! I had never had such delicious meat!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Anything else?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd185 f=04]「I also liked the Gull's Nest in Seagull Village! The seafood dishes there are excellent～!」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd186 f=01]「Also, the meat pie shop near Sapphire Castle is great! I keep coming back for their pies...」[k]
[テオ f=13]「Wait... It's all food stores.」[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=31
[フレデリカ f=31]「...! (Ah!)」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd187 f=33]「No, no! There were lots of good places besides food stores! For example, umm... Let's see...」[k]
@se f=guuu
@fg c=フレデリカ f=32
∗rumble∗[k]
[フレデリカ f=32]「... (Kyaaaa)」[k]
Suddenly, a loud noise rang out from [フレデリカ]'s belly.[k]
[テオ f=01]「Hahaha, you must be hungry. Actually, I am too. Let's go get something to eat in town now.」[k]
[フレデリカ f=25]「...!」[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=23
[フレデリカ v=vd188 f=23]「Yes, Captain!」[k]
[フレデリカ] replies cheerfully, I knew she was hungry.[k]
Afterwards, the two of us filled our stomachs at a restaurant in town.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
[hoteloff]


