[name f=other_02]I give [フレデリカ] the hair clip I bought in town.[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd195 f=05]「Is this...?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's a hair clip. I happened to find it in town and thought it would look good on you. You always tie your hair up in a bun, right? I thought you might use it.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd196 f=05]「...You're giving it to me?」[k]
