@fg c=フレデリカ f=52
[フレデリカ v=vd198 f=52]「...Sorry! That isn't possible!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「[フレデリカ]?」[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=29
[フレデリカ v=vd199 f=53]「I can't wear this... I'm sorry, Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「E-eh...?」[k]
She refused to accept my gift... Maybe I was presumptuous... Or maybe she doesn't like me...?[k]
[テオ f=13]「Didn't you like it...? I'm sorry for giving you a boring present.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd200 f=29]「No, no! It's not that!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Eh?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd201 f=29]「The hair clip I always wear... It's a traditional accessory that every dwarf girl wears...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「It's a tradition?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd202 f=29]「So I'm not allowed to wear any other hair clips... It's a rule...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Like a family code?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd203 f=30]「Yes...」[k]
Oh, I see. Then this is no good...[k]
@fg c=フレデリカ f=24
[フレデリカ v=vd204 f=24]「But I'm glad you thought of me... I'll keep this hair clip...」[k]
She then lovingly held the hair clip I had given her to her chest.[k]
[テオ f=01]「You will take it?」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd205 f=23]「Yes... I can't wear it, but... I'll take good care of it...」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Thank you. I'm glad to hear that.」[k]
[フレデリカ v=vd206 f=24]「Captain... I love it...」[k]
[フレデリカ] hugs the hair clip I gave her. I'm happy that she's so happy. At one point I was surprised because I thought she had turned me down.[k]
But still, it's tough being a dwarf. I can't believe there are even codes for things like that.[k]
I felt a little sorry for [フレデリカ], who is always so innocent and naive.[k]
